message: Updated README with how to organise dataset directories.
Added easy installation by conda environment (and updated README to reflect this)
Fixed installation to include PLIP library from GitHub
Updated README and point_vs.py to be consistent.

Introduced bi-headed model.

Classification training and regression finetuning can now be completed
in one command, without stopping, reloading and restarting training in
between.

New model class to support this goes by 'multitask' in training script.

Old models should still be compatible under 'egnn'.
Update README with MacOS Intel installation instructions.
Updated README to include regression types information
Enable MPS on Apple Silicon devices.
